Click here for my ask.fm - ask me a question; I'll answer just about any serious question.
Click here for my Twitter - I'll post good scores, stuff about beatmaps, and the rare time I stream.
Click here for my YouTube - footage of various rhythm games

Primary game/mode: osu!mania - 4 keys | 4K / 6K Beatmapper
Skin: Portalmania - get it here. // Downscroll Port by kiyoemon (give them a big thank you!)

About Mods
If I don't really know you well, or we don't talk on a regular basis, please do not ask me for one. It's not that I cannot do them, it's that I don't entirely appreciate being approached by someone to help them out when they don't have the courtesy to at least socialize with me. I barely mod as it is - thinking that you can get a mod out of me when others know they can't is a quick way to make sure that I ignore you.
